// Database Schema - Auto-synced from Supabase
// Last synced: 2026-01-26T19:32:44.130Z

Table AiCostData {
  id Int [pk, increment]
  totalCost Float [not null]
  updatedAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]
  chartUrl String
  csvUrl String
}

Table AiDailyCost {
  id Int [pk, increment]
  date DateTime [not null]
  cost Float [not null]
  createdAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]

  indexes {
    date [unique]
  }
}

Table ApkVersion {
  id Int [pk, increment]
  variant String [not null]
  version Int [not null]
  fileName String [not null]
  createdAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]

  indexes {
    variant [unique]
  }
}

Table DeviceProfileLink {
  id String [pk, default: `gen_random_uuid()`]
  deviceId String [not null]
  profileId String [not null]
  provider String [not null]
  createdAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]
  profileName String

  indexes {
    deviceId
    (provider, deviceId, profileId) [unique]
  }
}

Table SmsDeviceMapping {
  id String [pk, default: `gen_random_uuid()`]
  deviceId String [not null]
  displayName String [not null]
  phoneNumber String
  createdAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]
  updatedAt DateTime [not null]
  batteryPercentage Int
  lastPingAt DateTime
  undetectableProfileId String
  provider String
  installedApps String
  appVersionCode Int
  appVersionName String

  indexes {
    deviceId [unique]
  }
}

Table SmsMessage {
  id String [pk, default: `gen_random_uuid()`]
  deviceId String [not null]
  sender String [not null]
  body String [not null]
  timestamp DateTime [not null]
  receivedAt DateTime [default: `now()`]
  deviceName String
  phoneNumber String

  indexes {
    deviceId
    receivedAt
    sender
    timestamp
  }
}

Table SmsOutbound {
  id String [pk, default: `gen_random_uuid()`]
  deviceId String [not null]
  recipient String [not null]
  message String [not null]
  status String [not null, default: "pending"]
  error String
  createdAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]
  sentAt DateTime

  indexes {
    createdAt
    (deviceId, status)
  }
}

Table StatsSnapshot {
  id Int [pk, increment]
  leboncoin Int [not null, default: 0]
  superprof Int [not null, default: 0]
  whatsapp Int [not null, default: 0]
  ebay Int [not null, default: 0]
  vinted Int [not null, default: 0]
  fnac Int [not null, default: 0]
  cdiscount Int [not null, default: 0]
  amazon Int [not null, default: 0]
  finaryDispo Int
  fraisTech Int
  fraisIa Int
  createdAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]

  indexes {
    createdAt
  }
}

Table Task {
  id Int [pk, increment]
  componentName String [not null]
  componentDirectory String [not null]
  pageName String [not null]
  status String [not null, default: "Pending"]
  agentId String
  agentStatus String
  agentUrl String
  branchName String
  taskType String [not null, default: "component"]
  deploymentId String
  errorLogs String
  errorType String
  errorMessage String
  errorComponentPath String
  errorLineNumber Int
  errorIsAutoFixable Boolean [default: false]
  errorSeverity String
  errorDeploymentUrl String
  errorOriginalTask String
  errorOriginalAgentId String
  createdAt DateTime [not null, default: `now()`]
  completedAt DateTime
  updatedAt DateTime [not null]

  indexes {
    agentId
    branchName
    createdAt
    status
  }
}

// Relationships
Ref: DeviceProfileLink.deviceId > SmsDeviceMapping.deviceId [delete: cascade]
